high_descs: Turn left to the counter beside the sink.
Pick up the knife above the salt shaker.
Turn left and move left and face the small black counter.
Slice the potato on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the fridge.
Place the knife on the top row of the fridge.
Turn left and walk back to the small black counter.
Pick up one potato slice.
Turn left and walk back to the fridge.
Chill the potato slice in the fridge for 3 seconds.
Turn around and walk to face the microwave on the left.
Place the slice inside of the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled potato slice inside the microwave.

Walk with the knife towards the fridge
Put knife inside the fridge
Walk towards the small table
Grab a slice of potato from the table
Walk towards the fridge
Put the slice of potato inside the fridge and take it out
Walk with the potato slice towards the microwave
Put the potato slice inside the microwave
anns.task_desc: Slice a potato, put a slice inside the fridge, put it in the microwave
